      "text": "Tad fazzija Sauls us to rahdi to Nenoseedſigu/ tad tappe\nKUNGU to Israëta Deewu: Is-\nJonatans un Sauls eesihmeti/\nbet tee Laudis tsgahje (brthwi.)"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Sauls: Met- teet pahr mann un pahr mann\nDehlu Jonatanu/ tad tappe Jo-\nnatans eesihmehts."
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Sauls us\nJonatanu: Stahsti man/ ko tu\nfft darrijs? tad stahstija Jona-\ntans winnam/un fazzija: Es ef-\nnu tikai maſkenicht Meddu ban-\nijs ar manna Sisla Gassu/kaſ\nmannâ Rohkâ bija/ Reds/man\nuu jamirst."
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Sauls: Laid\nDeews man ſcha un ta darra/ Jo-\natans/ tew teefcham buhs mirt."
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tee Laudis us\nSaulu: Woj Jonatanam btj\nirt/ kaſ ſcho leelu Pestischanu\nktch Israëta padarrijs? Neba/\nik teefcham ka tas KUNGS\nfihiwo/ tam ne buhs Mats no\notna Galwas pee Seines kriſt/"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zehlehs Sauls no\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 47,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad usznehme Sauls to\nWalstibu pahr Israëlu/ un kar-\nroja wiﬀapkahrt ar wiﬀeem fa-\nweem Eenaidneekem/ arri prett\nMoabn/un prett Ammona Behr-\nneem/ un prett Eedomu/ un prett\nteem Kehnixeem no Jobas/ un\nprett teem Wilistexeem/ un wiﬀ-\nteem/ kurp wiꞥſch greesehs/ likke\nwiꞥſch ſawu Bahrsibu juſt."
    },
    {
      "n": 48,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fadabbuja\nSpehku/ un kawe tohs Amaleki-\nterus/ un iſpestija Israëlu no ta\nRohkas/ kaſ winnu aplaupija."
    },
    {
      "n": 49,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Saula Dehli bija Jo-\nnatans/ Iswus/ un Malkisuus/\nun teeWahrdi winna diwejo Mei-\nto/ tahs pirmdsintas Wahrdâ\nbija Merobe/ un tahs jaunakas\nWahrdâ bija Mikale."
    },
