      "n": 50,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Saula SeewasWahrdâ\nbija Afinoaine/ weena Meita A-\nkinaaza; un tas Wahrdâ winna\nKatra. Wirfneeka bija Abners/\nweens Dehls Nera/ Saula\nBrahlineeks."
    },
    {
      "n": 51,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Kis bija Saula Tehws/\nun Ners Abnera Tehws/ bija\nweens Dehls Abſeka."
